      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It has significant wear and damage on both the exterior and interior, including visible body damage, heavily worn upholstery, and cosmetic deterioration throughout. Mechanically it runs but has known issues consistent with its age and condition. Priced accordingly for a buyer willing to invest in repairs or use it for parts.",
